productReviews.reviewText: SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Analyst keeps them away.
I saw one of these in Cote d'Ivoire and I bought one.
I saw one of these in Haiti and I bought one.
My co-worker Mohamed has one of these. He says it looks brown.
I saw this on TV and wanted to give it a try.
